      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It runs super smoothly and is just waiting for someone new to take it on some adventures! If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
