    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly bridges the gap between high-end performance and everyday reliability. The exterior finish maintains a brilliant luster, having been frequently waxed, though a discerning eye will find a few small stone chips on the hood and a light scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical of respectful use. Step inside to a cabin that remains a sanctuary of comfort; the leather upholstery is supple and free of any punctures or unpleasant odors, showing only modest softening on the driver\u2019s seat bolsters. All onboard technology, including the high-resolution infotainment system, heated seats, and driver-assist features, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the vehicle has been maintained with an open checkbook. It features a complete service history with the most recent oil and filter change performed just 500 miles ago. The brakes are firm, the suspension is quiet over bumps, and the tires retain deep tread for all-season confidence. This car represents an excellent opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 31500.0,
